song.info: This is the first 17 or so minutes of my set and contains live-material from songs like the intro of the might pirate sessions #1 (Paul Shields), nukes chipshop, intromusic by 4mat Idas haschkaka, Botkyrka Sidekickers, Fyllecell Teenage Riot #4, Axwells Hybrid crackintro music RN85 & Såhärkanmanocksågöra (with zabutom). - Dubmood
